== Friendship Points ==
[[File:There Comes the Future Star Task Banner EN.png|500px]]

*After maintenance, {{Elite}} '''[[Li'l Sandy]]''' {{CL}} will provisionally join your fleet after you log into the game.
*You can collect '''"Friendship Points"''' by clearing normal mode story maps or [[Scherzo of Iron and Blood]] event maps during the event.
*By accumulating '''"Friendship Points"''', you can clear limited event missions and obtain rewards such as gold and items.
*'''[[Li'l Sandy]]''' will permanently join your fleet after you clear the last mission.
*'''IMPORTANT!''' <span style="color:red">'''If [[Li'l Sandy]] participates in and survives the boss battle, the amount of friendship points is doubled.'''</span>

